+------------------------+
|Useful emacs keybindings|
+------------------------+

M-<number>            Repeat next action n times (tested with character and
                      macro).

C-x z                 Repeat last command once.

M-%                   Query replace.

C-M-s                 Regex incremental search.

C-M-r                 Regex reverse incremental search.

C-x r d               Delete contents of rectangle.
                      Pushes text to the left.

C-x r c               Replace rectangle with spaces.

C-x r o               Insert blank space to fill rectangle.
                      Pushes text to the right.

C-x r t string <RET>  Replace rectangle contents with string on each line.